    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244020/extras/282538aef5481df377f4819e338d1c75.poster.avif?t=1696528865\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244020/extras/282538aef5481df377f4819e338d1c75.webm?t=1696528865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244020/extras/282538aef5481df377f4819e338d1c75.mp4?t=1696528865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Riley In The Abyss is a stealth action single-player game inspired by games and movies such as Alien, Deadspace, and Underwater. <br><br>You take the role of Riley, an Underwater engineering tech. She is positioned on the 4th level/ floor of an underwater research tower facility. Assisting scientists and researchers here, to embark on the unknown of the ocean's mysterious unexplored depths. <br>The entirety of the crew working in this section keeps reporting strange sounds beneath them. Bewildered and enthralled, crew members begin to contact teams in the lower sections of the research facility. Unbeknownst to any of the current events, Riley is asleep in her pod. <br><br>As she wakes up, head pounding, to her surprise everyone is...<br><br>Players will embark on a linear/free-roam story. They sneak and fight their way toward the elevator to exit this underwater facility. <br><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><i>Riley In The Abyss</i> provides deep storytelling, Environmental storytelling. Third-person shooting and stealth elements. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244020/extras/9bec330c78d7d0ab45a0af8c1ae49e45.poster.avif?t=1696528865\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea